{"title":"广场铜像","authors":["倪峻宇"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":11,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场铜像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倪峻宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回望家园的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年被交叉火力绞断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而曙色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自衣襟的弹洞溢出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫向四野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老母的呼唤渐远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡路的铃声渐远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卸下两肩硝烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座新生城市的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸽哨掠过。枪尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萌发一片祥和的蔚蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后的木棉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽放你理想的妍红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草坪铺开春意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一地童趣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站着。总是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在风雨的纷扰中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青苔，爬上你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十年的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军衣征尘未洗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在花季里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那仰视的虔诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正献上一片清纯"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}